Create a SImple Maven Project
Add selenium,WebDriverManager,testng,extendReport dependencies in pom.xml
Add surefire plugin in pom.xml



Calling the flush the method writes/updates the test information of your reporter to the destination type.
 otherwise, if you do not use this you will not see any error in your program because you won’t get any report.
 
 the extend report is created in the test-output folder where testng's index.html is generated as well.